{"info": {"author": "RUNIE", "author_email": "runar-borge@hotmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "description": "# ledworks\n\nledworks is a Python library for creating LED strip animations.\n\n\nExample animation class:\n```python\nclass HueComet(ledworks.Animation):\n    @ledworks.cycle(seconds=4.0, reverse=False)\n    def cycle(self, interval: float, led: ledworks.LEDContext):\n\n        color = ledworks.utils.hue(self.time * 1.61)\n        duration = randint(self.strip.count // 30, self.strip.count // 3) * interval\n\n        self.strip.assign(\n            led, ledworks.rate.fade(color=color, duration=duration)\n        )\n```\n\nAnd its output on the PygletPlayer:\n\n![HueComet](https://i.imgur.com/6G4gTey.gifv)\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/Run1e/ledworks", "keywords": "", "license": "", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "ledworks", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/ledworks/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/ledworks/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/Run1e/ledworks"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/ledworks/0.0.1/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": ">=3.6", "summary": "Library for creating LED strip animations.", "version": "0.0.1", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>ledworks</h1>\n<p>ledworks is a Python library for creating LED strip animations.</p>\n<p>Example animation class:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"k\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\">HueComet</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ledworks</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Animation</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n    <span class=\"nd\">@ledworks</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">cycle</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">seconds</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mf\">4.0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">reverse</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">False</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"nf\">cycle</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">interval</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"nb\">float</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">led</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ledworks</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">LEDContext</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n\n        <span class=\"n\">color</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">ledworks</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">utils</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hue</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">time</span> <span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"mf\">1.61</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">duration</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">randint</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">strip</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">count</span> <span class=\"o\">//</span> <span class=\"mi\">30</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">strip</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">count</span> <span class=\"o\">//</span> <span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">interval</span>\n\n        <span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">strip</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">assign</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n            <span class=\"n\">led</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">ledworks</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rate</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">fade</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">color</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">color</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">duration</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">duration</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p>And its output on the PygletPlayer:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"HueComet\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/a2eb753a6693941ca4232f67ac35790018cba623/68747470733a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f364734675465792e67696676\"></p>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 7102662, "releases": {"0.0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "07e75a48be5e7e8d5da9acd8d3b9651b", "sha256": "7aa50109be44c4c5fb8b553788fe1b5667dd01d5f75c12ffec725c2804df3751"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "ledworks-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "07e75a48be5e7e8d5da9acd8d3b9651b", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": ">=3.6", "size": 6599, "upload_time": "2020-04-26T04:03:17", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-26T04:03:17.751410Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/1b/66/aa92de2c570db70e23490a8fa6988e6c57ce83df5524d4e49e0671d03cbb/ledworks-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "75d0d53865b867e1eb26ea3ca9ed9151", "sha256": "97524818e852ede188a48fc8fbb469b5a95facca19f10eef4a4184331a274c78"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "ledworks-0.0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "75d0d53865b867e1eb26ea3ca9ed9151", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": ">=3.6", "size": 4669, "upload_time": "2020-04-26T04:03:19", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-26T04:03:19.891690Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/52/7b/9a830e93a01dd0307b985c56eab